n=1,2,3,\dots
\cos(x+iy) = \cos x \cosh y - i \sin x \sinh y
|\cos(x+iy)|^2 = \cos^2 x \cosh^2 y + \sin^2 x \sinh^2 y = \dfrac{\cos(2x)}{2} + \dfrac{\cosh(2y)}{2}
x = \pm n \pi \pm y
\cos(2x) = \cos(2y)
