|x+iy|=n\pi
|\cos(x+iy)|^2 \ge 1
|\cos(x+iy)|^2 = \frac{\cos(2y)+\cosh(2y)}{2} = \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{(2y)^{4n}}{(4n)!} \ge 1
